flowchart TD
    Start["Tool Invocation"] --> Mode{"Permission Mode?"}

    Mode -->|default| Rules["Check Permission Rules<br/>(allow/deny/ask)"]
    Mode -->|plan| PlanCheck["Read-only tools only"]
    Mode -->|auto| AutoPath["Auto Mode Path"]
    Mode -->|bypassPermissions| BypassCheck["Bypass Kill Switch"]
    Mode -->|acceptEdits| EditCheck["CWD Check"]

    Rules -->|allow rule matches| Allow["✅ ALLOW"]
    Rules -->|deny rule matches| Deny["❌ DENY"]
    Rules -->|no match / ask| Prompt["👤 Prompt User"]

    AutoPath --> Whitelist{"In SAFE_YOLO_<br/>ALLOWLISTED_TOOLS?<br/>(25+ tools)"}
    Whitelist -->|yes| Allow
    Whitelist -->|no| Classifier["YOLO Classifier"]

    Classifier --> Stage1["Stage 1: Fast<br/>max_tokens=64<br/>stop=['&lt;/block&gt;']"]
    Stage1 -->|allow| Allow
    Stage1 -->|block or unparseable| Stage2["Stage 2: Thinking<br/>max_tokens=4096<br/>&lt;thinking&gt; CoT"]
    Stage2 -->|allow| Allow
    Stage2 -->|block| Deny
    Stage2 -->|API error| FailClosed["❌ BLOCK<br/>(fail-closed)"]
    Stage2 -->|parse error| FailClosed

    BypassCheck -->|kill switch ON| Prompt
    BypassCheck -->|kill switch OFF| AutoPath

    EditCheck -->|inside CWD| Allow
    EditCheck -->|outside CWD| Classifier

    PlanCheck -->|read-only tool| Allow
    PlanCheck -->|write tool| Deny

    Prompt -->|user allows| Allow
    Prompt -->|user denies| DenialTrack["Denial Tracking"]
    DenialTrack -->|consecutive < 3<br/>total < 20| Deny
    DenialTrack -->|threshold reached| FallbackPrompt["Fallback to<br/>interactive prompting"]

    style Allow fill:#4CAF50,color:#fff
    style Deny fill:#f44336,color:#fff
    style FailClosed fill:#f44336,color:#fff
    style Classifier fill:#2196F3,color:#fff
    style Stage1 fill:#2196F3,color:#fff
    style Stage2 fill:#2196F3,color:#fff
